Robert E. Radway



Mr. Robert E. Radway is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at NXT Capital LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at CDK Global, Inc. 
Mr. Radway was previously employed as Founder by Merrill Lynch Capital Corp., a Principal by FINOVA Group, Inc., President by GE HFS Holdings, Inc., and EVP-Corporate Strategy & Development by Heller Financial, Inc. 
He received his undergraduate degree from Syracuse University and an MBA from Santa Clara University.



