Executive Profile
Robert E. Radway  Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, NXT Capital, LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships57--
Background

		Mr. Robert E. Radway serves as the Chief Executive Officer and Chairman at NXT Capital, LLC. Mr. Radway served as the Managing Director and President at Merrill Lynch Capital Inc. at Merrill Lynch & Co., Inc. He led the formation and development of Merrill Lynch Capital from its inception in 2001 until 2008 where he was responsible for all aspects of the business. Prior to that, Mr. Radway held senior positions at Heller Financial, Inc., including Executive Vice President ... of Corporate Strategy and Development where he was responsible for its worldwide strategic planning, business development and merger and acquisitions worldwide. He also served as a Group President at Heller Healthcare Finance where he structured and negotiated its sale in 2001. Mr. Radway’s held a number of executive positions at The Finova Group including Executive Vice President and Head of the Capital Markets Group. He also worked at Business Property Lending, Inc. He has been an Independent Director of CDK Global, Inc. since September 30, 2014. Mr. Radway holds an M.B.A. from the University of Santa Clara and a B.S. from Syracuse University.Read Full Background




